OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJapan court upholds ban on 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsame-sex marriage          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Tokyo court has upheld a ban on      
OL,6, same-sex marriage in Japan, but also   
OL,7, said that the ban was a violation of   
OL,8, human rights.                          
OL,10,FThe compensation case was brought by   
OL,11,Ffour couples who claimed the law was   
OL,12,Fdiscriminatory.                        
OL,14,FJapan is currently the only G7 nation  
OL,15,Fthat does not recognise same-sex       
OL,16,Fmarriage.                              
OL,18,FCampaigners have welcomed the ruling as
OL,19,Fan indication to the government that it
OL,20,Fneeds to change the law.               
